   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 21,
   "id": "e0439b84-c6b6-4ca6-a43d-bd53dc2c28b2",

      "text/plain": [
       "<AxesSubplot: ylabel='Count'>"
      ]

     "execution_count": 21,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1200x400 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "vv = [run.effect.value for run in runs]\n",
    "sns.histplot(vv, kde=True)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c5b4a339-be9a-4d44-acd2-f892383ee218",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
